1
00:00:31,010 --> 00:00:33,270
[You Have My Heart]

2
00:00:33,290 --> 00:00:36,120
[Episode 7
By Faces We Pledge]

3
00:00:43,950 --> 00:00:45,030
I, Wan,

4
00:00:46,700 --> 00:00:48,700
beg an audience with the Magistrate

5
00:00:49,900 --> 00:00:51,430
to seek justice.

6
00:00:52,720 --> 00:00:53,850
Aren't you dead?

7
00:01:02,980 --> 00:01:03,620
My Lord.

8
00:01:04,190 --> 00:01:05,190
Stay away from me!

9
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:07,000
Stay away from me!

10
00:01:08,340 --> 00:01:08,980
My Lord,

11
00:01:10,780 --> 00:01:12,060
I am Wan.

12
00:01:21,340 --> 00:01:22,200
You are warm.

13
00:01:24,240 --> 00:01:25,200
You're alive.

14
00:01:29,070 --> 00:01:31,070
Then who's the one dead in that room?

15
00:01:51,380 --> 00:01:52,979
You like this face very much.

16
00:01:55,310 --> 00:01:56,240
Very beautiful,

17
00:01:56,590 --> 00:01:57,340
isn't it?

18
00:01:59,009 --> 00:02:00,340
It is indeed beautiful.

19
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:03,770
As expected of a masterpiece
of your making.

20
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:05,790
Not just mine.

21
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:07,460
We did it together.

22
00:02:18,750 --> 00:02:21,060
You have been nourished
in the pool for a long time.

23
00:02:21,060 --> 00:02:22,920
Your mind has long since cleared.

24
00:02:23,430 --> 00:02:24,560
Playing dumb with me

25
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:27,560
is pointless.

26
00:02:28,920 --> 00:02:31,290
I... I wouldn't dare.

27
00:02:32,020 --> 00:02:33,900
The corpse in Huichun Brothel

28
00:02:34,650 --> 00:02:35,640
is Mingyuan.

29
00:02:54,329 --> 00:02:55,430
It is Mingyuan.

30
00:02:57,329 --> 00:02:58,210
This scar,

31
00:02:58,840 --> 00:03:00,050
she got it one year

32
00:03:00,890 --> 00:03:03,490
when she accidentally
knocked over a brazier.

33
00:03:45,450 --> 00:03:47,640
We had everything prepared.

34
00:03:49,610 --> 00:03:51,520
Why did it end like this?

35
00:03:56,500 --> 00:03:57,160
Madam Chun.

36
00:03:57,850 --> 00:04:00,380
Since you're certain
the victim is Mingyuan,

37
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:02,520
why did you misidentify her before?

38
00:04:02,790 --> 00:04:03,510
My Lord.

39
00:04:04,110 --> 00:04:06,050
The body was mutilated so horribly,

40
00:04:06,050 --> 00:04:08,100
I couldn't bear to look at it closely.

41
00:04:08,100 --> 00:04:09,220
I only saw

42
00:04:09,630 --> 00:04:11,360
she was wearing Wan's clothes,

43
00:04:11,410 --> 00:04:13,250
so I assumed it was Wan.

44
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:15,250
Wan.

45
00:04:16,450 --> 00:04:17,829
Since you're not the victim,

46
00:04:17,829 --> 00:04:19,459
why haven't you come to the county yamen

47
00:04:19,459 --> 00:04:21,660
to clear this up for days after the case?

48
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:23,360
My Lord.

49
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,060
For the past five days,

50
00:04:27,670 --> 00:04:30,110
I've been staying in Lin County
with Mr. Du.

51
00:04:32,070 --> 00:04:32,800
Mr. Du?

52
00:04:34,070 --> 00:04:35,200
Mingyuan's patron?

53
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:36,870
You two...

54
00:04:36,870 --> 00:04:37,720
No.

55
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:40,920
It's not what you think, My Lord.

56
00:04:42,950 --> 00:04:44,600
I went with Mr. Du

57
00:04:46,760 --> 00:04:48,320
for Mingyuan's sake.

58
00:04:49,950 --> 00:04:51,680
The women of Yin-Yang Crossing

59
00:04:51,870 --> 00:04:54,800
have their own ways
of making themselves beautiful.

60
00:04:56,670 --> 00:04:59,600
Some ask the Dagger Spirit
to refine their features,

61
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:03,080
while others let the Face-Weaving Spider
plump their looks.

62
00:05:03,450 --> 00:05:05,050
But Mingyuan was different.

63
00:05:06,630 --> 00:05:08,030
She was a natural beauty,

64
00:05:08,510 --> 00:05:10,470
and relied on her original face

65
00:05:10,660 --> 00:05:13,320
to become the top courtesan
of Huichun Brothel.

66
00:05:13,780 --> 00:05:17,110
She used to despise
those artificial cosmetic procedures.

67
00:05:17,390 --> 00:05:18,430
But this year,

68
00:05:20,850 --> 00:05:23,510
she also started sighing
in front of the mirror.

69
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:26,630
About a month ago,

70
00:05:27,630 --> 00:05:29,290
I noticed that her appearance

71
00:05:29,340 --> 00:05:30,940
had quietly begun to change.

72
00:05:32,510 --> 00:05:33,510
At first,

73
00:05:34,450 --> 00:05:37,250
her eyes were just bigger
and brighter than usual.

74
00:05:38,510 --> 00:05:39,190
Later,

75
00:05:40,060 --> 00:05:42,659
her lips also became unusually full
and plump.

76
00:05:43,750 --> 00:05:44,480
I knew

77
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:47,260
she eventually, like everyone else,

78
00:05:47,580 --> 00:05:48,530
found a way.

79
00:05:50,190 --> 00:05:52,120
This wouldn't have been a big deal.

80
00:05:52,350 --> 00:05:53,880
But even after the changes,

81
00:05:53,980 --> 00:05:56,310
she felt it wasn't enough
a few days later,

82
00:05:56,930 --> 00:05:58,460
and started sighing again.

83
00:05:59,180 --> 00:06:00,440
Constantly comparing herself

84
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:02,440
to the younger girls in the brothel,

85
00:06:03,850 --> 00:06:05,210
She became obsessed.

86
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:15,550
Mr. Du truly adores Mingyuan.

87
00:06:17,370 --> 00:06:19,570
He couldn't bear
to see her in such pain.

88
00:06:19,910 --> 00:06:20,910
So we agreed

89
00:06:22,640 --> 00:06:25,770
that he would go home
to sell his antiques and paintings,

90
00:06:26,740 --> 00:06:29,170
and I would lead the way
to my hometown in Lin County

91
00:06:29,170 --> 00:06:30,880
to buy a quiet courtyard.

92
00:06:31,710 --> 00:06:34,780
We wanted to take Mingyuan
away from Huichun Brothel,

93
00:06:35,310 --> 00:06:36,970
away from Yin-Yang Crossing.

94
00:06:37,909 --> 00:06:39,159
Everything has been arranged.

95
00:06:39,159 --> 00:06:41,490
This is ultimately a prison for her heart.

96
00:06:41,670 --> 00:06:42,800
Let's take her away.

97
00:06:46,470 --> 00:06:47,670
This is too precious.

98
00:06:47,900 --> 00:06:48,580
Mr. Du,

99
00:06:48,830 --> 00:06:49,590
just keep it.

100
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:53,380
It is better that you give it to Mingyuan.

101
00:06:57,840 --> 00:07:00,440
It happened to be
Mingyuan's birthday soon,

102
00:07:01,300 --> 00:07:02,380
so we thought

103
00:07:02,640 --> 00:07:03,770
we'd keep it a secret

104
00:07:04,190 --> 00:07:05,520
as a birthday surprise.

105
00:07:06,140 --> 00:07:07,400
Who would have thought

106
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:10,260
that there was a murder
right after we came back.

107
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:12,000
I was the one dead.

108
00:07:13,990 --> 00:07:16,590
Mingyuan was suspected
of being the murderer,

109
00:07:18,830 --> 00:07:20,360
and also went missing.

110
00:07:28,180 --> 00:07:29,390
So Mingyuan

111
00:07:29,930 --> 00:07:32,810
also cares deeply about her looks.

112
00:07:39,510 --> 00:07:40,240
Shopkeeper.

113
00:07:41,510 --> 00:07:43,800
Has anyone come to your shop recently

114
00:07:43,909 --> 00:07:44,800
to buy arsenic?

115
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:47,560
Arsenic.

116
00:07:48,950 --> 00:07:49,750
A few days ago,

117
00:07:49,780 --> 00:07:51,040
a woman came to my shop.

118
00:07:51,390 --> 00:07:53,150
She first asked for some wound ointment.

119
00:07:53,150 --> 00:07:54,460
Halfway through getting it,

120
00:07:54,460 --> 00:07:55,630
she suddenly changed her mind

121
00:07:55,630 --> 00:07:57,480
and said, "forget it,
give me some arsenic instead."

122
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:58,360
Nothing else.

123
00:08:01,870 --> 00:08:02,750
Did this woman

124
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:05,240
have any distinguishing features?

125
00:08:06,050 --> 00:08:07,650
She was young and wore a veil.

126
00:08:08,990 --> 00:08:09,590
Oh, right.

127
00:08:09,710 --> 00:08:11,100
Her voice and figure

128
00:08:11,440 --> 00:08:14,300
were somewhat like Mingyuan
from Huichun Brothel.

129
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:15,870
I once had the honor

130
00:08:15,870 --> 00:08:18,330
of seeing Miss Mingyuan's graceful figure.

131
00:08:19,190 --> 00:08:21,050
Truly unforgettable at a glance.

132
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:23,390
That's why I remember that woman

133
00:08:23,410 --> 00:08:24,470
a bit more clearly.

134
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:25,600
Is that the point?

135
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:27,280
Just sell your medicine!

136
00:08:27,300 --> 00:08:27,770
Okay.

137
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:31,430
So Mingyuan herself bought the arsenic.

138
00:08:32,500 --> 00:08:34,700
Could it be that she committed suicide?

139
00:08:36,070 --> 00:08:38,669
The Mirror Spirit can take on
Mingyuan's form.

140
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:39,750
Have you forgotten?

141
00:08:39,750 --> 00:08:40,549
That's right.

142
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:45,460
Then it's really hard to say
who actually bought it.

143
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:47,030
But why

144
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:49,320
did she need wound ointment?

145
00:08:50,590 --> 00:08:51,790
Perhaps...

146
00:08:51,820 --> 00:08:53,700
Why switch to arsenic later?

147
00:09:00,030 --> 00:09:01,870
If I were Lord Bai right now,

148
00:09:02,820 --> 00:09:04,150
how would I deduce this?

149
00:09:10,500 --> 00:09:13,380
Wound ointment reduces swelling,
stops bleeding,

150
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:16,160
regenerates tissue, and clears sores.

151
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:18,520
What else can it do?

152
00:09:20,750 --> 00:09:21,790
All I know is

153
00:09:22,190 --> 00:09:24,190
that it cannot cure a brain illness.

154
00:09:24,430 --> 00:09:26,430
Stop posturing and wasting time.

155
00:09:26,640 --> 00:09:27,970
Just go back and report.

156
00:09:31,190 --> 00:09:32,640
Who's the one posturing?

157
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:39,790
Beautiful.

158
00:09:51,020 --> 00:09:52,520
This is Face-Weaving Spider.

159
00:09:52,520 --> 00:09:56,180
He specializes in spinning silk
to plump up skin and lift the face.

160
00:09:56,590 --> 00:09:59,050
This is the new county magistrate,
Lord Bai.

161
00:10:02,610 --> 00:10:04,870
The Mirror Spirit used to work under you?

162
00:10:05,390 --> 00:10:06,150
My Lady,

163
00:10:06,610 --> 00:10:08,140
Jing was once my assistant.

164
00:10:08,560 --> 00:10:09,690
What happened then?

165
00:10:10,740 --> 00:10:11,800
Jing loves beauty.

166
00:10:12,160 --> 00:10:13,890
After meeting someone better,

167
00:10:14,300 --> 00:10:16,070
she naturally abandoned me.

168
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:17,960
Thank you.

169
00:10:19,180 --> 00:10:20,180
I'll walk you out.

170
00:10:24,920 --> 00:10:25,520
Take care.

171
00:10:45,140 --> 00:10:46,940
I come for Face-Weaving Spider.

172
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:48,200
I heard

173
00:10:48,520 --> 00:10:50,440
he can make people look younger.

174
00:10:55,680 --> 00:10:58,680
Miss,
the price of this skin-filling technique

175
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:00,240
is too high.

176
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:03,120
The more you refine, the weaker it gets.

177
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:04,190
In a few months,

178
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:06,160
you'll find your skin

179
00:11:06,750 --> 00:11:08,280
much older than it is today.

180
00:11:09,770 --> 00:11:12,170
I have heard those words.

181
00:11:13,760 --> 00:11:14,550
But I...

182
00:11:16,940 --> 00:11:18,610
What if there's a better way?

183
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:23,240
Everyone has a love for beauty.

184
00:11:24,790 --> 00:11:26,520
But if it becomes an obsession,

185
00:11:27,350 --> 00:11:28,810
one will gradually forget

186
00:11:28,930 --> 00:11:30,880
what true beauty is.

187
00:11:32,780 --> 00:11:33,550
I never thought

188
00:11:33,550 --> 00:11:34,960
that the Mirror Spirit and Mingyuan

189
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:36,760
would share such a deep history.

190
00:11:37,070 --> 00:11:37,620
It seems

191
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:40,560
she is still our best breakthrough point
for this case.

192
00:11:40,560 --> 00:11:42,090
When investigating in Yin-Yang Crossing,

193
00:11:42,090 --> 00:11:44,370
you must consider things more deeply.

194
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:49,210
Thank you for the advice, Lady Fufeng.

195
00:11:49,790 --> 00:11:50,850
Consider it a debt.

196
00:11:52,500 --> 00:11:53,930
When you owe me more...

197
00:11:57,270 --> 00:11:57,960
Then what?

198
00:12:03,670 --> 00:12:06,000
You'll stay here and pay them back slowly.

199
00:12:33,770 --> 00:12:36,170
Mingyuan has been taken by Wan and Mr. Du

200
00:12:36,390 --> 00:12:38,140
to her new residence for burial.

201
00:12:38,140 --> 00:12:39,140
Before they left,

202
00:12:39,650 --> 00:12:41,180
I restored her appearance.

203
00:12:43,860 --> 00:12:45,790
What happened to Mingyuan's face?

204
00:12:46,220 --> 00:12:47,080
Mirror Spirit,

205
00:12:47,760 --> 00:12:48,810
you still try to deny it

206
00:12:48,810 --> 00:12:49,850
at this point?

207
00:12:50,330 --> 00:12:52,050
You were jealous of Mingyuan's beauty,

208
00:12:52,050 --> 00:12:53,910
so you disfigured and killed her.

209
00:12:54,090 --> 00:12:54,950
Nonsense!

210
00:12:55,950 --> 00:12:57,950
I would rather die than hurt her.

211
00:12:59,590 --> 00:13:01,280
She was my only friend.

212
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:03,150
Friend?

213
00:13:09,010 --> 00:13:10,740
We refined this face together.

214
00:13:11,680 --> 00:13:13,480
This is our shared masterpiece,

215
00:13:14,740 --> 00:13:16,620
and our shared secret.

216
00:13:40,150 --> 00:13:41,480
By blood we seal,

217
00:13:41,720 --> 00:13:43,000
mirrored as one heart.

218
00:13:43,480 --> 00:13:44,600
By faces we pledge,

219
00:13:44,790 --> 00:13:46,190
renewed year after year.

220
00:13:58,390 --> 00:14:00,390
I can become anyone I've seen.

221
00:14:01,570 --> 00:14:03,770
Now, look at your own face.

222
00:14:07,630 --> 00:14:08,630
You can tell me

223
00:14:08,900 --> 00:14:10,700
what you're not satisfied with.

224
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:13,600
What good would it do to tell you?

225
00:14:33,360 --> 00:14:33,910
It

226
00:14:36,370 --> 00:14:37,300
really changed.

227
00:14:40,330 --> 00:14:41,590
How should I thank you?

228
00:14:43,470 --> 00:14:44,040
I...

229
00:14:45,630 --> 00:14:46,690
I don't want money.

230
00:14:49,200 --> 00:14:51,360
I only wish to borrow this face of yours

231
00:14:51,870 --> 00:14:53,000
to go out for a while.

232
00:14:54,850 --> 00:14:56,380
I want to feel what it's like

233
00:14:57,070 --> 00:14:58,870
to be looked at with admiration.

234
00:15:00,310 --> 00:15:02,570
Mingyuan was the first person
willing to light a lamp at night

235
00:15:02,570 --> 00:15:03,650
and wait for me.

236
00:15:04,450 --> 00:15:06,220
Her obsession grew deeper.

237
00:15:07,460 --> 00:15:10,290
She kept saying
she wanted to become more beautiful.

238
00:15:10,290 --> 00:15:12,290
But she was already very beautiful.

239
00:15:13,520 --> 00:15:16,760
If she changed further,
she would no longer be herself.

240
00:15:17,840 --> 00:15:18,770
She always said,

241
00:15:20,440 --> 00:15:21,870
''It does not matter if I lose myself.''

242
00:15:21,870 --> 00:15:23,800
It does not matter if I lose myself.

243
00:15:24,600 --> 00:15:26,400
As long as people still adore me,

244
00:15:27,450 --> 00:15:30,520
as long as no one leaves me.

245
00:15:33,630 --> 00:15:35,430
If the masterpiece is finished,

246
00:15:36,030 --> 00:15:37,790
she won't need you anymore.

247
00:15:38,380 --> 00:15:39,530
She will leave.

248
00:15:40,170 --> 00:15:42,600
She will go after the one she loves.

249
00:15:43,340 --> 00:15:44,340
By then,

250
00:15:44,800 --> 00:15:47,130
you won't be able to become her anymore.

251
00:15:47,630 --> 00:15:48,540
Right?

252
00:15:48,790 --> 00:15:49,520
No.

253
00:15:50,250 --> 00:15:51,560
She won't leave me.

254
00:15:51,700 --> 00:15:53,030
You're too naive.

255
00:15:53,780 --> 00:15:57,510
Find a way to make her stay.

256
00:15:58,140 --> 00:16:01,930
Find a way to make her stay.

257
00:16:02,210 --> 00:16:02,850
Jing,

258
00:16:03,200 --> 00:16:04,460
what's wrong with you?

259
00:16:10,710 --> 00:16:12,240
You're scaring me a little.

260
00:16:17,760 --> 00:16:19,000
I don't remember.

261
00:16:19,320 --> 00:16:20,390
I don't remember.

262
00:16:23,380 --> 00:16:23,910
My Lady.

263
00:16:23,910 --> 00:16:25,110
My head hurts so much.

264
00:16:31,330 --> 00:16:32,750
My Lady, your...

265
00:16:52,780 --> 00:16:54,580
I don't remember what happened.

266
00:16:56,670 --> 00:16:58,550
I looked at the face in the mirror

267
00:16:59,320 --> 00:17:01,250
and just thought it was beautiful.

268
00:17:01,720 --> 00:17:03,850
But I didn't even recognize who it was.

269
00:17:04,550 --> 00:17:07,410
I've been staying at Xiqianhua
these past few days.

270
00:17:07,589 --> 00:17:11,030
Lady Fufeng restored my consciousness
with the spiritual spring.

271
00:17:11,030 --> 00:17:12,290
Then I remembered her.

272
00:17:14,050 --> 00:17:15,970
I thought Mingyuan had run away.

273
00:17:16,440 --> 00:17:17,890
I didn't want you to catch her,

274
00:17:17,890 --> 00:17:18,609
so

275
00:17:19,589 --> 00:17:21,450
I pretended to remember nothing.

276
00:17:23,240 --> 00:17:24,050
So...

277
00:17:25,369 --> 00:17:26,569
So her face...

278
00:17:28,250 --> 00:17:29,100
It was me.

279
00:18:10,470 --> 00:18:11,190
It was me.

280
00:18:12,640 --> 00:18:13,840
It was the evil power.

281
00:18:14,340 --> 00:18:17,140
Because your mind was corrupted
by the evil power,

282
00:18:17,160 --> 00:18:19,880
you accidentally disfigured Mingyuan.

283
00:18:20,740 --> 00:18:22,350
I killed her.

284
00:18:24,960 --> 00:18:27,510
Her pupils were dilated,
the root of her tongue turned black,

285
00:18:27,510 --> 00:18:28,770
and her blood was dark.

286
00:18:29,090 --> 00:18:30,750
These are signs of poisoning.

287
00:18:31,450 --> 00:18:32,710
She must have applied wound ointment

288
00:18:32,710 --> 00:18:33,910
after being injured.

289
00:18:34,990 --> 00:18:37,030
But a few days later,
when she looked in the mirror

290
00:18:37,030 --> 00:18:38,590
and saw her ruined face,

291
00:18:39,240 --> 00:18:40,370
her mind shattered.

292
00:18:40,750 --> 00:18:42,600
She took poison and ended her own life.

293
00:18:42,600 --> 00:18:43,930
As for her other wounds,

294
00:18:44,290 --> 00:18:45,650
she inflicted them on herself

295
00:18:45,650 --> 00:18:47,680
with the mirror, cut by cut.

296
00:19:05,970 --> 00:19:06,690
As for

297
00:19:07,420 --> 00:19:09,350
why she was wearing Wan's clothes,

298
00:19:09,510 --> 00:19:11,510
it's because she didn't want anyone

299
00:19:11,950 --> 00:19:13,480
to recognize her as the once

300
00:19:13,950 --> 00:19:15,750
famed courtesan of the region--

301
00:19:16,320 --> 00:19:17,040
Mingyuan.

302
00:19:46,030 --> 00:19:46,490
My Lady,

303
00:19:47,010 --> 00:19:48,940
I have something to ask you.

304
00:19:49,750 --> 00:19:50,270
Speak.

305
00:19:51,040 --> 00:19:54,110
The Mirror Spirit masters the art
of altering appearances.

306
00:19:54,110 --> 00:19:55,450
Why did she only decide to change faces

307
00:19:55,450 --> 00:19:56,850
after meeting Mingyuan?

308
00:20:00,230 --> 00:20:02,360
Because she thought she was unworthy.

309
00:20:02,960 --> 00:20:05,000
Even if she could easily
change her appearance,

310
00:20:05,000 --> 00:20:07,660
she had to repeatedly
find reasons for herself.

311
00:20:08,440 --> 00:20:09,570
Just like Mingyuan,

312
00:20:10,830 --> 00:20:13,400
clearly a famous beauty
in Yin-Yang Crossing,

313
00:20:13,400 --> 00:20:15,400
yet because she was slightly older,

314
00:20:15,640 --> 00:20:17,900
she changed her appearance at all costs.

315
00:20:19,390 --> 00:20:21,270
They both have extraordinary qualities,

316
00:20:21,270 --> 00:20:23,870
yet are consumed
by the dread of fading beauty.

317
00:20:24,920 --> 00:20:26,040
This human and this spirit,

318
00:20:26,040 --> 00:20:27,950
could share the exact same agony.

319
00:20:31,920 --> 00:20:32,480
My Lady,

320
00:20:32,870 --> 00:20:34,190
once this case is over,

321
00:20:34,620 --> 00:20:37,280
how will Xiqianhua deal
with the Mirror Spirit?

322
00:20:38,160 --> 00:20:39,640
She will be punished according to the law.

323
00:20:39,640 --> 00:20:42,180
After the punishment,
she will stay in Xiqianhua

324
00:20:42,180 --> 00:20:43,100
to work for me.

325
00:20:44,080 --> 00:20:44,990
Work for you?

326
00:20:47,350 --> 00:20:47,790
Yes.

327
00:20:48,750 --> 00:20:49,310
For me.

328
00:20:52,980 --> 00:20:53,700
What?

329
00:20:55,630 --> 00:20:56,830
Do you want to as well?

330
00:21:01,060 --> 00:21:02,900
My Lady, who exactly wants that?

331
00:21:20,690 --> 00:21:21,540
I don't.

332
00:21:24,960 --> 00:21:26,310
This case is closed,

333
00:21:26,510 --> 00:21:29,350
but evil power lies behind all of this.

334
00:21:30,930 --> 00:21:32,130
Keep investigating.

335
00:21:35,090 --> 00:21:35,680
Yes.

336
00:21:36,370 --> 00:21:37,570
Come see me tomorrow,

337
00:21:38,030 --> 00:21:38,880
late at night.

338
00:21:44,550 --> 00:21:45,160
My Lady,

339
00:21:46,480 --> 00:21:47,790
then I won't bother you further.
